

Q3
Return all reviewer names and movie names together in a single list, alphabetized.
SELECT title
FROM Movie
UNION
SELECT name
FROM reviewer
ORDER BY name, title

Q4
1/1 point (ungraded)
Find the titles of all movies not reviewed by Chris Jackson. 


SELECT DISTINCT title
FROM movie m
WHERE mid not in (SELECT r.mid
FROM Rating r
JOIN reviewer v
ON r.rid= v.rid
WHERE name = "Chris Jackson")

--- advanced
SELECT
    TITLE
FROM Movie m LEFT JOIN Rating r ON r.mID=m.mID
LEFT JOIN Reviewer v ON v.rID=r.rID
GROUP BY TITLE
HAVING MAX(IF(name = 'Chris Jackson', 1, 0)) = 0



Q5
1/1 point (ungraded)
For all pairs of reviewers such that both reviewers gave a rating to the same movie, return the names of both reviewers. Eliminate duplicates, don't pair reviewers with themselves, and include each pair only once. For each pair, return the names in the pair in alphabetical order. 
select DISTINCT v1.name, v2.name
FROM rating r1
JOIN reviewer v1
ON r1.rid=v1.rid
JOIN rating r2
ON r2.mid=r1.mid
JOIN reviewer v2
ON v2.rid= r2.rid
WHERE v1.name < v2.name
